{"tid":1167091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為副董事長徐直軍於美國被控幫助偷取商業秘密","createTime":"2019-05-23T00:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T03:56:59.000Z","uid":131691,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1d0ffa6364f18ad172f97ed4c5522b66b7882049","tid":1167091,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T00:15:25.000Z","msg":"The Verge: Huawei executive accused of helping steal trade secrets.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2019/5/22/18636237/huawei-cnex-trade-secrets-lawsuit-eric-xu-accusation-trial-hearing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2019%2F5%2F22%2F18636237%2Fhuawei-cnex-trade-secrets-lawsuit-eric-xu-accusation-trial-hearing&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo7Y5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=0cfc9aaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theverge.com/2019/5/22/18636237/huawei-cnex-trade-secrets-lawsuit-eric-xu-accusation-trial-hearing</a>"},{"pid":"9152ce0f13a58bf76c73fa71cca670e746681ea2","tid":1167091,"uid":3083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T00:27:53.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<br />\n<br />\n不過遲下支那又會捉番幾個美國人，希望侵侵會凍結哂仆街嘅資產"},{"pid":"10241b276a15d9397163d65d504811e958fbf4de","tid":1167091,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T00:29:14.000Z","msg":"《華爾街日報》引述法庭文件稱，美國一間晶片初創企業指控華為副董事長Eric Xu，涉及合謀偷取該公司的商業機密。<br />\n<br />\n案件將於6月3日在得克薩斯州聯邦法庭開審。<br />\n<br />\n原訴CNEX Labs指控華為在中國一間大學協助下，涉及進行為期多年的合謀行動，偷取集團的機密。根據CNEX陳述的案情，該公司正研發一項有助數據中心所用電腦硬件提升效能的技術，華為在一名中國大學教授協助下，非法掌握了有關技術。CNEX與華為自2017年開始便出現爭拗。<br />\n<br />\n華為與CNEX未有回應傳媒相關查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2144208\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2144208&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo7Y5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=90b423d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2144208</a>"},{"pid":"94e1dabb6d8478c4a85162103064fc51fb69fdfe"